## Mobile Responsive Considerations

### Mobile Dashboard
- Collapsed sidebar accessible via hamburger menu
- Focus on key metrics and quick actions
- Simplified navigation with bottom tab bar

### Mobile Content Generation
- Full-screen input mode for writing prompts
- Simplified style controls with expandable sections
- Bottom sheet for quick settings

### Mobile Corpus Management
- List view with cards for each document
- Pull-to-refresh for updates
- Floating action button for uploads

## Animation and Interaction Design

### Microinteractions
- Subtle hover states for interactive elements
- Progress indicators for long-running processes
- Success animations for completed actions

### Page Transitions
- Smooth fade transitions between pages
- Slide transitions for related content
- Scale transitions for modal dialogs

### Loading States
- Skeleton screens for content loading
- Animated spinners for processing actions
- Progress bars for uploads and generations

## Accessibility Considerations

- Color contrast ratios meeting WCAG AA standards
- Support for screen readers with proper ARIA labels
- Keyboard navigation for all interactive elements
- Focus indicators for keyboard users
- Text scaling without breaking layouts
